						<p><hi rend="bold">King: Vīranarasiṅga. Year: <hi rend="italic">Vikrama, Mārgaḻi</hi> 22.</hi></p>						

						<p>Built in. This inscription is in characters of the 15th century A.D. Records that a certain person Sūryadē ••••, an agent of Vīranarasiṅgarāya-nāyakkar made a gift of 7 <hi rend="italic">mā</hi> and 1(1/2) <hi rend="italic">kāṇi</hi> of land, freed from taxes, <hi rend="italic">(sarvamānya)</hi> for the merit of Vīranarasiṅgarāyar.</p>						

